{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 122800, "create_time": 1652848681, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "@天火哥\n来解答下", "timestamp": 1652848681}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 122844, "create_time": 1652849564, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "第二题还好吧，词缀很明显，词缀的辅音会被词根末的辅音同化，词缀的元音也和词根元音有对应关系。", "timestamp": 1652849564}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 122884, "create_time": 1652850789, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 2, "text": "ikbalsiz, takatsiz\nsütçü, gözsüz, dilci, dilsiz, kalɪpçɪ, kalɪpsɪz", "timestamp": 1652850789}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 122887, "create_time": 1652850830, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 2, "text": "四组元音和谐，cç清浊根据词根末音同化。", "timestamp": 1652850830}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 122889, "create_time": 1652850889, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: 天火哥第一个怎么看的", "timestamp": 1652850889}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 122896, "create_time": 1652850972, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 元音和谐不对", "timestamp": 1652850972}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 122897, "create_time": 1652850990, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Alice: 哦艹，是因为i是前高元音，a是后低元音，不和谐吗", "timestamp": 1652850990}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 122899, "create_time": 1652851041, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "我还以为左边放一个外来词，右边放一个外来词，是我想多了", "timestamp": 1652851041}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 122904, "create_time": 1652851101, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Alice: 并不，其实这两个在有元音和谐的语言里很多时候都是中性元音。关键是这里a和ɪ和谐三次，a和i和谐两次，既然只有两个是外来词那就只能是那两个了。", "timestamp": 1652851101}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 122909, "create_time": 1652851270, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Dave: 好家伙，我还在想a前后可能分不太清，没想到找规律还要数数，这就是语奥吗，天火哥威武", "timestamp": 1652851270}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 122924, "create_time": 1652851730, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Alice: 其实证据不止这些。你可能也会以为güre那个可能是外来词，因为ü和e不和谐，但从这几个例子并不能百分百地确定元音和谐的范围是不是局部的。但是如果你对历史有点了解的话就会知道，土耳其语，尤其是奥斯曼土耳其语从波斯语借了大量的词，而波斯语（实际上整个印度-伊朗语族）有一个出了名的音位垃圾桶/a/，那当然是a出现多的更有可能是借词，而ü这样的音几乎是借不到的。", "timestamp": 1652851730}], "create_time": 1652848656, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1652851730, "likenum": 8, "n_attentions": 8, "n_comments": 11, "pid": 43471, "poll": null, "reply": 11, "text": "#语奥\n#简单版\n![](https://bafkreidpnwj4jjmtfcln52eoge4dswb2xxbez2dwtk4amvvxwqnyzjso7m.ipfs.hub.textile.io/?filename=v2-b7613f43dc7f20c0f01e2e91e9b96722_r.jpg&filetype=image%2Fjpeg) [加载失败请点击此](https://hole-thu.github.io/ipfs.html#bafkreidpnwj4jjmtfcln52eoge4dswb2xxbez2dwtk4amvvxwqnyzjso7m)\n\n---\n", "timestamp": 1652848656}}